{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "66bcbd82ae81d148616b11e1", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 1, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 60, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76e4c52ffa3c944600e1"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eb95"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "64b850012a7d64ecd80b00a1", "title": "NEET 2002", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "Which of the following is best close to an ideal black body?", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "5McPE", "text": "Black lamp", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "k4D8u", "text": "Cavity maintained at constant temperature", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "VN3IL", "text": "Platinum black", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "Bex2N", "text": "A lamp of charcoal heated to high temperature", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "An ideal black body is one which absorbs all the incident radiation without reflecting or transmitting any part of it. Black lamp absorbs approximately \\(96 \\%\\) of incident radiation.\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/neet/vpNFKxqZE86caDjLfzgSroR_2.png\">\r\nAn ideal black body can be realized in practice by a small hole in the wall of a hollow body (as shown in figure) which is at uniform temperature. Any radiation entering the hollow body through the holes suffers a number of reflections and ultimately gets completely absorbed. This can be facilitated by coating the interior surface with black so that about \\(96 \\%\\) of the radiation is absorbed at each reflection. The portion of the interior surface opposite lo the hole is made conical to avoid the escape of reflected ray after one reflection.", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGNEPYQ89196008", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "updatedAt": "2024-08-30T08:17:47.374Z", "updated_by": "65d0c176a8f74604505ba6f6", "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023e599225f756e5df101", "616023e3445073e7f19122db", "61bb8229fce3576e46202d7d", "616023e0ffc8649daddda513", "61e7bd7f80092b5aa328b5a1", "616023e23a74832357599443", "616023e361589c931bc035b7", "61964c81150b027922bafad8", "61c089b4384657354ede4c09", "61964c81e74f86f9041974e2", "629f390e0537a44301966fe8", "629621250160e8ee846a120c", "629109f1da1b4d5a11b7952f", "629f3a930c61425b93824746", "64eb06bf3118f713ecfef06f", "66d58553a75f05ee8564f668", "67921d611d5b5072da5e9a8e", "67fdff4f378e1624ea7b69fd", "680920293a10446a207fdec5"], "cpyqbExams": ["616059d70283de43c87e3e24", "616059730283de43c87e3e22"]}}